<mjml>
  <mj-include path="./head.mjml" />
  <mj-body mj-class="body">
    <mj-wrapper background-color="#F0F0F0">
      <mj-section />
      <mj-section css-class="section">
        <mj-column>
          <mj-text mj-class="headline"
            >You have received an application from ${menteeFullName}!</mj-text
          >
          <mj-divider mj-class="divider-top" css-class="divider" />

          <mj-text mj-class="text" padding="0 0 20px 0"
            >Hi ${mentorName},</mj-text
          >
          <mj-text mj-class="text paragraph"
            >You have received a mentee application from
            <strong>${menteeFullName}</strong> from
            <strong>ReDI ${locationNameFormatted}</strong>! Here is a message
            from them:
          </mj-text>
          <mj-text mj-class="text quote">${menteeApplicationText}</mj-text>
          <mj-text mj-class="text" padding="20px 0"
            >Please log into ReDI Connect to review this application and visit
            the profile of the mentee at your earliest convenience:</mj-text
          >
          <mj-button
            href="${applicationsPageUrl}"
            background-color="#F15A22"
            color="#fff"
            font-size="16px"
            font-weight="bold"
            border-radius="4px"
            padding="16px 24px"
            align="center"
            line-height="120%"
            text-decoration="none"
          >
            Review Application
          </mj-button>
          <mj-text mj-class="text"
            ><strong>After reviewing the application:</strong></mj-text
          >
          <mj-text mj-class="text">
            <ul>
              <li>
                If you would like to become their mentor, please
                <strong>accept the application</strong> and suggest a date and
                time for your first meeting, either online or in person. You may
                also share your preferred contact methods (email, links, etc.).
              </li>
              <li>
                If you realize that you cannot support them in the way they need
                or are currently too busy to take on new mentees, please
                <strong>decline the application</strong> and add a brief message
                explaining why.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </mj-text>
          <mj-text mj-class="text paragraph"
            >Additionally, remember that you can set your mentee count capacity
            to '0' in your profile. This will make your profile invisible to
            mentees until you change it back when you are ready to accept
            applications again.</mj-text
          >

          <mj-text mj-class="text">All the best,</mj-text>
          <mj-text mj-class="text">ReDI Malm√∂ Team</mj-text>
        </mj-column>
      </mj-section>
      <mj-include path="./footer.malmo.team.mjml" />
      <mj-section />
    </mj-wrapper>
  </mj-body>
</mjml>
